<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>HTML Tags Demo</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Main Heading</h1>
    <h2>Sub Heading</h2>

    <p>
        This is a paragraph.
        <b>This text is bold.</b><br>
        <i>This text is italic.</i><br>
        <u>This text is underlined.</u>
    </p>

    <p>
        Superscript Example: x<sup>2</sup> + y<sup>2</sup>
    </p>

    <p>
        Subscript Example: H<sub>2</sub>O and CO<sub>2</sub>
    </p>

</body>
</html>
